data.description: Step inside this lovely updated 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home located in North Philadelphia. The main room is spacious and bright, with big windows bringing in lots of natural light. Throughout the home, you'll find calming neutral colors.  On the first floor, there's a cozy living room, a dining area perfect for family meals, and a kitchen with a gas stove, lots of cabinet space, and modern tiling. Upstairs, there's a full bathroom with a linen closet, and three comfy bedrooms, including a large primary bedroom for relaxation.  Stay comfortable all year round with heat radiators for winter warmth and window unit AC for summer coolness. Outside, there's a private backyard for gatherings and a front porch to unwind.  The basement offers plenty of storage space and includes a washer and dryer. Conveniently located near major roads, lots of restaurants, Hunting Park, and just a short drive to Center City. Schedule your tour today and make this charming house your home! (This property may qualify for down payment assistance programs up to $10,000!)
